Historical International Station Catalogue

STN #         - THE 6-DIGIT STATION NUMBER (FIRST 5 DIGITS CORRESPOND   
                TO WMO NUMBER IF ONE EXISTS)
        
CALL          - THE STATION'S CALL LETTERS, IF USED
  
NAME          - THE STATION'S NAME   

COUNTRY/STATE - 2 CHARACTER ABBREVIATION FOR COUNTRY, FOR U.S.--
                THE STATE POSTAL ID 

LAT           - LATITUDE IN DEGREES AND MINUTES   

LON           - LONGITUDE IN DEGREES AND MINUTES  

ELEV          - ELEVATION IN METERS  

DATE          - THE LATEST DATE (AS YEAR-MONTH) FOR THAT UNIQUE STATION  
                ENTRY INTO THE CATALOG.  NOT AN INDICATION OF THE
                STARTING OR ENDING DATE FOR CLIMATIC DATA.
